name: Lame Boi
description:
This is a Lame Boi. There is nothing unique or interesting about a Lame Boi, they're just lame. However, you can burn your Lame Boi and take your chances at Get Dope or Get Dead, where your Lame Boi will either end up getting dope or getting dead. Don't be lame. Burn your boi.

Get Dope or Get Dead is a manual process, so the outcome will not happen immediately after burning your Lame Boi. We will be checking regularly for burned Lame Bois, but you can also DM us on Twitter or Discord when you burn a Lame Boi. For more info on the Dope Bois Project and a link to the Dope Bois Discord check out @dopeboisnft on Twitter.
